{
  "api": "Retently API v2 (https://app.retently.com/api/v2)",
  "docs": "https://www.retently.com/api/",
  "reviewed_at": "2026-07-03",
  "scope": "wave2 fan-out migration: the 4 legacy-parity read streams only (customers, responses, surveys, campaigns); legacy ships no writes (capabilities.write is false) and the full Retently surface (feedback import, transactional survey queueing, templates, NPS/CSAT/CES score endpoints, campaign reports) is out of scope until Pass B.",
